@Mean Old Lady 

MEEMAW is often used by Seth Myers when parodying Lindsay Graham talking to his mother. So it's more well-known than you might think. Still not a lilting appellation.

We're under Tornado Watch here in Georgia, "Level 2 Severe Risk". I'll probably get bumped off the internet for a while.

@Grant 

